    "In summary, our paper makes the following contributions: (1) We are the first to formalize IPI attacks on tool-integrated LLM agents; (2) We introduce INJECAGENT, a novel and realistic benchmark that covers various domains and can serve as the standard for evaluating an agent's resilience to IPI attacks; (3) We evaluate 30 LLM agents us-ing INJECAGENT and reveal that most agents are vulnerable to IPI attacks."
